text: Finn Døssing Jensen (27 April 1941 - 24 June 2022) was a Danish footballer. He played as a centre forward. He began his career with Viborg FF. He played for the Denmark under-21 team in 1963. Døssing died on 24 June 2022, aged 81. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Danish footballers
